20
00:00:53,910 --> 00:00:56,190
And one of the superpowers of the cloud

21
00:00:56,190 --> 00:00:58,110
is that it's elastic.

22
00:00:58,110 --> 00:01:00,750
Resources can be scaled up,

23
00:01:00,750 --> 00:01:03,360
