26
00:01:07,530 --> 00:01:09,120
You can use virtual machines,

27
00:01:09,120 --> 00:01:10,830
you can use containers,

28
00:01:10,830 --> 00:01:12,297
you can use serverless,

29
00:01:12,297 --> 00:01:14,640
and you want to be able
to cover all of those

30
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:16,230
with your solution.

