37
00:01:31,650 --> 00:01:33,390
Some of the traditional solutions

38
00:01:33,390 --> 00:01:37,230
also ask you to license
each of your resources.

39
00:01:37,230 --> 00:01:38,280
Well, how do you do that

40
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:39,690
