48
00:01:57,270 --> 00:01:59,370
You scan again on Tuesday,

49
00:01:59,370 --> 00:02:01,080
you have another thousand.

50
00:02:01,080 --> 00:02:02,520
How do you deal with all those?

51
00:02:02,520 --> 00:02:06,300
How do you prioritize the
findings that you're getting?

