00:02:08,190 --> 00:02:10,050
You could look at the severity,

54
00:02:10,050 --> 00:02:11,730
start with the criticals,

55
00:02:11,730 --> 00:02:13,200
but more and more,

56
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:15,450
there are a lot of critical
vulnerabilities out there

57
00:02:15,450 --> 00:02:18,390
and they may not be the
most important ones for you

58
00:02:18,390 --> 00:02:22,413
to remediate based off
of your environment.

