61
00:02:30,870 --> 00:02:33,030
and we created Amazon Inspector

62
00:02:33,030 --> 00:02:36,360
to be an automated
vulnerability management service

63
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:39,570
that continually monitors your workloads

64
00:02:39,570 --> 00:02:41,490
for software vulnerabilities

65
00:02:41,490 --> 00:02:44,340
and unintended network exposures.

66
00:02:44,340 --> 00:02:46,140
And you can see that we've highlighted

67
00:02:46,140 --> 00:02:49,620
two really key features
of Inspector right here.

68
00:02:49,620 --> 00:02:51,240
One is automated.

69
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:54,300
