00:10:43,500 --> 00:10:46,590
We package all of our
vulnerability information

239
00:10:46,590 --> 00:10:47,610
into a format

240
00:10:47,610 --> 00:10:50,610
where you can search it for yourself.

241
00:10:50,610 --> 00:10:53,359
You can look at CVEs, you can know,

