00:10:53,359 --> 00:10:56,370
okay, does Inspector know about the CVE?

243
00:10:56,370 --> 00:10:58,350
What are the details?

244
00:10:58,350 --> 00:10:59,430
Is it a high?

245
00:10:59,430 --> 00:11:00,930
Is it a low?

246
00:11:00,930 --> 00:11:04,890
I can check to see what type
of resources it impacts.

247
00:11:04,890 --> 00:11:07,350
And I can also immediately know

248
00:11:07,350 --> 00:11:10,890
which of my resources
are impacted by this.

